    <innerclass refid="class_gaze_1_1_projection_engine" prot="public">Gaze::ProjectionEngine</innerclass>
    <innernamespace refid="namespace_gaze">Gaze</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Ray-Plane Projection Engine and Calibration Solver (Layer 4). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implements the mathematical models for projecting raw 3D gaze rays onto physical screen planes, incorporating offset, resolution, and tilt parameters. Computes analytical calibration offsets (both 3D angular biases and 2D pixel offsets) and estimates focal depth from eye distance. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
